1
00:00:00,560 --> 00:00:04,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}THREE DAYS AFTER THE RETURN
OF THE PURIFICATION EXPEDITION</font>

2
00:00:02,540 --> 00:00:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondou-san!</font>

3
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-san.</font>

4
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for all you've done on 
all three purification expeditions.</font>

5
00:00:10,420 --> 00:00:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so welcome!</font>

6
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My humblest gratitude for purifying 
the miasma, Your Holiness.</font>

7
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thank you from the bottom of my heart.</font>

8
00:00:22,390 --> 00:00:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, Shiraishi-san...</font>

9
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to hear about the expedition.</font>

10
00:00:27,230 --> 00:00:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why don't we have lunch together?</font>

11
00:00:29,540 --> 00:00:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to hear about the progress 
on the cram school, as well.</font>

12
00:00:32,580 --> 00:00:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you care to join us, Siegvold-san?</font>

13
00:00:34,910 --> 00:00:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

14
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to make sure
 the disciple eats his meals.</font>

15
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop calling me that. 
My name is Kondou Seiichirou.</font>

16
00:00:45,410 --> 00:00:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you are the disciple...</font>

17
00:00:47,810 --> 00:00:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It attracts too much attention.</font>

18
00:00:49,730 --> 00:00:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You leave me little choice. 
I shall compromise.</font>

19
00:00:53,410 --> 00:00:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro.</font>

20
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very good, Reverend.</font>

21
00:00:57,230 --> 00:01:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I conceded first. Please call me 
by my first name, as well.</font>

22
00:01:02,790 --> 00:01:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood, Siegvold-sama.</font>

23
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:24,890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ISEKAI OFFICE WORKER: THE OTHER WORLD'S 
BOOKS DEPEND ON THE BEAN COUNTER</font>

24
00:02:37,130 --> 00:02:41,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 10: I INVESTIGATED</font>

25
00:02:39,070 --> 00:02:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a beautiful place!</font>

26
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The holy maiden of two generations 
ago created this flower garden.</font>

27
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea this was here!</font>

28
00:02:47,510 --> 00:02:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't need a lunch?</font>

29
00:02:49,510 --> 00:02:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

30
00:02:50,530 --> 00:02:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondou-san has to be mindful of 
what he eats or he'll overdose.</font>

31
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

32
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro has no 
resistance to magicules.</font>

33
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he must be careful with
 his diet and lifestyle.</font>

34
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magicules give you strength so 
long as you don't absorb too much,</font>

35
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they're everywhere! Like air!</font>

36
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He came from a world unlike ours.</font>

37
00:03:12,650 --> 00:03:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The air and food there 
must have been different.</font>

38
00:03:15,250 --> 00:03:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What about Your Holiness?</font>

39
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I seem to be blessed with divine 
protection, so I'm unaffected.</font>

40
00:03:21,950 --> 00:03:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro has been 
suffering this tribulation,</font>

41
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet he still works hard for our kingdom.</font>

42
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please treat him with care.</font>

43
00:03:29,970 --> 00:03:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't paint a weird image of me.</i></font>

44
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, Selio-san.</font>

45
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been slowly gaining some resistance,</font>

46
00:03:38,610 --> 00:03:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I won't die unless I absorb 
a large amount of magicules.</font>

47
00:03:42,810 --> 00:03:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could die?!</font>

48
00:03:46,550 --> 00:03:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-san, could you tell me
 about the purification expedition?</font>

49
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

50
00:03:51,410 --> 00:03:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were no changes during 
the first and second expeditions,</font>

51
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but once the miasma was gone, 
light poured onto the tree,</font>

52
00:03:59,550 --> 00:04:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and buds sprouted on part of it.</font>

53
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're apparently proof that 
the purification is complete.</font>

54
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard that the sorcerers
 are now recording</font>

55
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">below-normal levels of magicules there.</font>

56
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when they investigated 
the surrounding area,</font>

57
00:04:15,490 --> 00:04:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they found the footprints 
of a beast called a nepolic.</font>

58
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-san wanted to dispatch it at once.</font>

59
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It takes three days to reach the 
demon forest from the royal capital.</i></font>

60
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Staying out was more efficient
 than returning.</i></font>

61
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would've done the same thing.</i></font>

62
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

63
00:04:37,890 --> 00:04:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu-sama, you have 
a letter from Aresh-sama.</font>

64
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nepolics have rather large territories, 
so our hunt is taking some time.</i></font>

65
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You have nothing to worry about. 
Just take care of your own health.</i></font>

66
00:04:58,730 --> 00:05:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's smart and talented.</i></font>

67
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Though he's a cold beauty with a way
of speaking that makes him seem mature,</i></font>

68
00:05:04,550 --> 00:05:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he's surprisingly childish at home and
 sulks if you don't pay attention to him.</i></font>

69
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He always wears a guilty expression 
when Valtom-san scolds him.</i></font>

70
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When he has work he doesn't want to do, 
he ends up clinging to me even more,</i></font>

71
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as if smothering his reluctance to go.</i></font>

72
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's why he took on this 
sudden subjugation mission.</i></font>

73
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He wants me to praise him.</i></font>

74
00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Apart, I cannot help but 
marvel at our past unmet.</i></font>

75
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that we're apart,</i></font>

76
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't help wondering how I managed 
to live before meeting you...</i></font>

77
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about some fish?</font>

78
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro! Long time no see!</font>

79
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sigma-kun. How have things been?</font>

80
00:05:56,840 --> 00:06:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well, my boss hurt his hand, 
so I can't train under him right now.</font>

81
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's looking for a new place that'll 
take me, but since I'm just a kid...</font>

82
00:06:07,690 --> 00:06:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I keep getting brushed off.</font>

83
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect timing, then.</font>

84
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to make more 
of those calculators for me.</font>

85
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

86
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You pay real well, so that's great!</font>

87
00:06:20,970 --> 00:06:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many?</font>

88
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thirty of them.</font>

89
00:06:22,850 --> 00:06:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thirty?!</font>

90
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, Sigma-kun...</font>

91
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever thought
about going to school?</font>

92
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's Kondu.</font>

93
00:06:33,450 --> 00:06:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Something's different.</font>

94
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Different?</font>

95
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your magical energy's
different from normal...</font>

96
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

97
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The third order isn't around right now.</font>

98
00:06:43,590 --> 00:06:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right, Kondu!</font>

99
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you bring me a sacred relic?</font>

100
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a good memory
for such things.</font>

101
00:06:49,050 --> 00:06:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bid you also remember that 
I told you that'd be impossible.</font>

102
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you want one so badly?</font>

103
00:06:55,130 --> 00:06:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

104
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because those things have so much
 magical energy stored in them.</font>

105
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be able to do all the research
I wanted with that.</font>

106
00:07:02,850 --> 00:07:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They store magical energy?</i></font>

107
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Doesn't that make them magic tools?</i></font>

108
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ist-san, have you seen 
a sacred relic before?</font>

109
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have.</font>

110
00:07:13,890 --> 00:07:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You pray to them when you turn six.</font>

111
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, I have loads of magical energy.</font>

112
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>According to the prime minister, 
kids train to reduce their magical energy.</i></font>

113
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now the church has a sacred relic
to collect said magical energy.</i></font>

114
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where exactly is that energy going?</i></font>

115
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something feels off. Where should 
I start investigating first?</i></font>

116
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sei-san, did you finish up 
with the sorcery department?</font>

117
00:07:40,810 --> 00:07:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nor, perfect timing. There's 
something I want to ask you...</font>

118
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kondu.</font>

119
00:07:46,350 --> 00:07:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

120
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something I wish 
to ask you. Come with me.</font>

121
00:07:53,730 --> 00:07:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll just be on my way...</font>

122
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Join us.</font>

123
00:07:58,210 --> 00:07:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

124
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you spoke at great length
with Yua the other day.</font>

125
00:08:05,810 --> 00:08:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. We were discussing 
Her Holiness's work.</font>

126
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me the details!</font>

127
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then please take a look
 at this document here.</font>

128
00:08:14,850 --> 00:08:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall!</font>

129
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A private school for</font>

130
00:08:19,230 --> 00:08:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the almshouse children and 
the poor children of the city...</font>

131
00:08:23,230 --> 00:08:26,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Her Holiness really 
come up with this?</font>

132
00:08:26,530 --> 00:08:29,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This kind of flawless, pragmatic plan
feels like something you would—</font>

133
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd expect no less from Yua! 
What a brilliant idea!</font>

134
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why didn't she mention it to me?</font>

135
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was probably planning to share it
with you once her plan came together.</font>

136
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, for Your Highness in all your
wisdom to catch on ahead of time</font>

137
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and fulfill her wishes
 by supporting her cause...</font>

138
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's exactly what I wanted.</i></font>

139
00:08:51,590 --> 00:08:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! You're absolutely right!</font>

140
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was actually thinking the same thing!</font>

141
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me and Yua are totally on the same page!</font>

142
00:08:57,310 --> 00:09:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's so excited, he started 
talking casually.</i></font>

143
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree.</font>

144
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, should you support her with your own
funds instead of the national treasury,</font>

145
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would further emphasize 
your stance on the matter</font>

146
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and make you dependable in her eyes.</font>

147
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how things work in our world.</font>

148
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, is that so?!</font>

149
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I was thinking of doing just that!</font>

150
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall go speak with Yua at once!</font>

151
00:09:27,730 --> 00:09:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sei-san, are you planning to make this
happen with His Highness's personal funds?</font>

152
00:09:32,190 --> 00:09:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kingdom's budget is tight right now.</font>

153
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, it's true that my 
country values self-sacrifice.</font>

154
00:09:41,010 --> 00:09:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must be how they raise 
workaholics like you, Sei-san.</font>

155
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu, enjoy these with the rest 
of the accounting department.</font>

156
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is His Highness aware of this?</font>

157
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness gave me the order.</font>

158
00:09:55,530 --> 00:09:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't believe me, do you?</font>

159
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness may greatly 
admire Her Holiness,</font>

160
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he is also a worthy heir as 
the first in line for the throne.</font>

161
00:10:07,230 --> 00:10:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yurius and Nor, the illegitimate 
son who was adopted out,</i></font>

162
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>are both children of the current 
king and biological brothers.</i></font>

163
00:10:17,250 --> 00:10:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Treats from His Highness?</font>

164
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really loved these as a kid.</font>

165
00:10:22,370 --> 00:10:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

166
00:10:24,290 --> 00:10:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So he's aware of his 
little brother's likes?</i></font>

167
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, wasn't there 
something you wanted to ask me?</font>

168
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes.</font>

169
00:10:31,830 --> 00:10:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've seen a sacred 
relic before, haven't you?</font>

170
00:10:35,650 --> 00:10:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A sacred relic? Yeah, I have.</i></font>

171
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those statues with magic
crystals in them, right?</i></font>

172
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And as for magical energy...</i></font>

173
00:10:42,830 --> 00:10:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They absorb it, right?</i></font>

174
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that common knowledge?</i></font>

175
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Only the royal family and 
the bishop know about it.</i></font>

176
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's actually a secret, 
but I figure it's fine if you know.</i></font>

177
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That makes it a state secret.</i></font>

178
00:10:57,340 --> 00:11:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No wonder different people say 
different things about it.</i></font>

179
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happens to the magical 
energy once it's collected?</font>

180
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's used for the barrier that protects
the royal capital from magic beasts.</font>

181
00:11:08,970 --> 00:11:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The barrier around the royal 
capital is kinda special.</font>

182
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can even repel magic attacks 
from other countries.</font>

183
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who would've thought
not only the prime minister,</i></font>

184
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:21,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but even Aresh-sama was unaware of this?</i></font>

185
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The barrier around the 
royal capital must be</i></font>

186
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>constantly replenished 
with magical energy.</i></font>

187
00:11:26,660 --> 00:11:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where the Church comes in.</font>

188
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their sacred relic has a magic tool
 embedded in it to convert</i></font>

189
00:11:33,850 --> 00:11:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the prayers of the people 
into offerings of magical energy.</i></font>

190
00:11:40,950 --> 00:11:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as I suspected...</font>

191
00:11:43,130 --> 00:11:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's an unnatural bump.</font>

192
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've learned three things.</i></font>

193
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:51,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>First, the church is collecting
the magical energy</i></font>

194
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>of people's prayers and 
storing it in a sacred relic.</i></font>

195
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Second, that magical energy is being used
for the barrier defending the capital.</i></font>

196
00:11:58,570 --> 00:12:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Third, the kingdom gives 
financial support to the Church,</i></font>

197
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>including a provision for magical energy.</i></font>

198
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Furthermore, it seems some of this magical
energy was used to summon the holy maiden.</i></font>

199
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, there's no record of the
exact amount spent in the process.</i></font>

200
00:12:18,050 --> 00:12:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even though it's kept secret, 
it's a recognized source of energy.</i></font>

201
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since it's generating money,
I need more detailed information on it.</i></font>

202
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro, you don't 
look well. Are you all right?</font>

203
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

204
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But your face looks pale...</font>

205
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Siegvold-san! And Kondou-san!</font>

206
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning!</font>

207
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shira— Your Holiness and...</font>

208
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness?</font>

209
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to stand on ceremony.</font>

210
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall allow you to call me "Yuri" 
when I am dressed like this.</font>

211
00:13:08,930 --> 00:13:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondou-san!</font>

212
00:13:10,170 --> 00:13:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri-sama says he'll help 
support the cram school!</font>

213
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was thinking of doing
 the same thing I wanted to</font>

214
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and decided to come check out 
the almshouse incognito today!</font>

215
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As expected. Men in love move fast.</i></font>

216
00:13:23,350 --> 00:13:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu! Give us the rundown and a tour!</font>

217
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, yes.</font>

218
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you be all right?</font>

219
00:13:32,540 --> 00:13:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

220
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Holiness!</font>

221
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Selio-kun.</font>

222
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Who's that?</font>

223
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro! Thank goodness you're here.</font>

224
00:13:49,590 --> 00:13:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sigma-kun? What are you doing here?</font>

225
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I told my mom 
about the private school,</font>

226
00:13:55,430 --> 00:13:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she told me to hurry up and get in on it
before the nobility changes their mind.</font>

227
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect timing.</font>

228
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With both children of the almshouse 
and common folk here,</font>

229
00:14:05,690 --> 00:14:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can better explain 
things to our sponsor.</font>

230
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sponsor?</font>

231
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's another term for an investor. 
I mean that man over there.</font>

232
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm no noble myself, but he's <i>very</i>
 important, so tread carefully.</font>

233
00:14:20,870 --> 00:14:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your relationship with this kid?</font>

234
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I recruited Sigma-kun here
from a street stall downtown.</font>

235
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:33,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's an amazing boy who's
smart, creative, and proactive.</font>

236
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Bro...</font>

237
00:14:36,730 --> 00:14:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't I tell you, Selio?</font>

238
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the kind of man the 
disciple—Master Seiichiro is.</font>

239
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be swayed by the talk and 
preconceptions of those around you.</font>

240
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look with your own eyes
and decide things for yourself.</font>

241
00:14:51,730 --> 00:14:53,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With my own eyes...</font>

242
00:14:57,860 --> 00:14:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I am.</font>

243
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ist-san? Why are you here?</font>

244
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

245
00:15:03,930 --> 00:15:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dropped by yesterday and looked 
at all sorts of documents,</font>

246
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I thought you'd be here
 checking out the sacred relic.</font>

247
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you guys already pray today?</font>

248
00:15:14,270 --> 00:15:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

249
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet.</font>

250
00:15:16,130 --> 00:15:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. In that case, 
can I tag along with all of you?</font>

251
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

252
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's here for prayer...</i></font>

253
00:15:24,470 --> 00:15:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In other words, to observe the supply 
of magical energy to the sacred relic.</i></font>

254
00:15:29,410 --> 00:15:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro, might this man be...</font>

255
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Ist-san, the assistant director
of the royal sorcery department.</font>

256
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Ist, welcome 
to the Church of Abran.</font>

257
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A handshake! He wants to shake your hand!</font>

258
00:15:47,130 --> 00:15:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello!</font>

259
00:15:49,950 --> 00:15:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can imagine how difficult
Director Zoltan has it.</i></font>

260
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to pray? I'll come too, then.</font>

261
00:15:58,180 --> 00:15:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-san...</font>

262
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you been to pray before?</font>

263
00:16:02,180 --> 00:16:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

264
00:16:03,170 --> 00:16:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I usually attend prayer when 
helping at the almshouse.</font>

265
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yua, you...</font>

266
00:16:07,570 --> 00:16:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

267
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri-sama?</font>

268
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Outside of practice,</i></font>

269
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>everyone makes sure she uses as 
little magical energy as possible,</i></font>

270
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>yet the church is extracting
magical energy from her</i></font>

271
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>when her top priority is the purification.</i></font>

272
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This very well may 
affect the purification.</i></font>

273
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It would seem the royal palace
was in the dark on this.</i></font>

274
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:40,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ist-san and I will attend the prayer.</font>

275
00:16:40,220 --> 00:16:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you would, hang back
and show Yuri-sama around.</font>

276
00:16:44,590 --> 00:16:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay...</font>

277
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yua, please be my guide.</font>

278
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

279
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let's go.</font>

280
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go? Go where?</font>

281
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To the sacred relic.</font>

282
00:16:59,190 --> 00:17:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

283
00:17:00,130 --> 00:17:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Outsiders must obtain permission 
from the bishop before entering.</font>

284
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:05,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

285
00:17:05,730 --> 00:17:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then could you please ask for permission?</font>

286
00:17:07,570 --> 00:17:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is so sudden...</font>

287
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind me. That guy from the 
sorcery department came here alone,</font>

288
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without an appointment, 
just to see the sacred relic.</font>

289
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You understand where this is going, right?</font>

290
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He won't listen even if you tell him no.</font>

291
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have no idea what he may do.</font>

292
00:17:26,870 --> 00:17:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get permission quickly.</font>

293
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be able to stall
him for very long.</font>

294
00:17:34,390 --> 00:17:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Kondu, I'm very sorry for the delay
 on the income and expenses report.</font>

295
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should be able to give 
it to you by tomorrow...</font>

296
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's fine, Brother Cipriano.</font>

297
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for causing you more 
trouble when you're so busy.</font>

298
00:17:51,210 --> 00:17:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll be done with the church tomorrow...</i></font>

299
00:17:54,970 --> 00:17:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That means I have to wrap things up today.</i></font>

300
00:17:59,900 --> 00:18:02,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the special prayer room.</font>

301
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As beautiful as I remember it...</font>

302
00:18:16,010 --> 00:18:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro?</font>

303
00:18:19,890 --> 00:18:23,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh! You've returned 
from the expedition.</font>

304
00:18:23,090 --> 00:18:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

305
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The third royal order has returned 
safely, without a single knight missing.</font>

306
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very good. Excellent work.</font>

307
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-san, welcome back.</font>

308
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is that guy?</font>

309
00:18:34,610 --> 00:18:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"That guy"? Oh, Kondu?</font>

310
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He went to the prayer room
with the almshouse children.</font>

311
00:18:40,470 --> 00:18:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That can't be...</font>

312
00:18:41,630 --> 00:18:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean where the sacred relic is housed?</font>

313
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was little, I couldn't 
control my magical energy,</font>

314
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:52,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I began to believe 
that I was a devil's child.</font>

315
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:56,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I was brought to this prayer room,</font>

316
00:18:56,800 --> 00:19:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where I prayed to Abran 
and regained control.</font>

317
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that moment, I swore to serve 
him for the rest of my life.</font>

318
00:19:08,280 --> 00:19:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Didn't his condition just calm down 
because the extra magical energy</i></font>

319
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>flowing out of him was absorbed?</i></font>

320
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

321
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

322
00:19:16,740 --> 00:19:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... I was just thinking the way 
they're praying is different from before.</font>

323
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you've prayed before?</font>

324
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Five years ago at my baptism.</font>

325
00:19:27,170 --> 00:19:29,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe things have changed since then?</font>

326
00:19:29,850 --> 00:19:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

327
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't like this before.</font>

328
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This method absorbs too 
much magical energy,</font>

329
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which could disrupt the 
body's magical circulation</font>

330
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and make the children lose control.</font>

331
00:19:41,330 --> 00:19:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

332
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't this a ritual to express 
gratitude for God's blessing?</i></font>

333
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like that priest can 
sense magical energy.</font>

334
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if they absorb 
this much every time now.</font>

335
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can tell how much 
magical energy there is?</font>

336
00:19:56,600 --> 00:20:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. The sorcery department tends 
to collect those of us sensitive to it.</font>

337
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro, are you a sorcerer?!</font>

338
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:03,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

339
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's awesome! I can't believe 
you can see magical energy!</font>

340
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be nice...</font>

341
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:09,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't tell at all.</font>

342
00:20:09,840 --> 00:20:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be cool if there was a tool 
to measure magical energy.</font>

343
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be even better if it could 
measure magical energy</font>

344
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in a way that even someone with 
no sense for it, like me, could see.</font>

345
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What shape would it take? 
A device worn over the eye?</font>

346
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you look through it like glasses?</font>

347
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, that would be fine if it
were for a single person,</font>

348
00:20:29,570 --> 00:20:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if you're making it...</font>

349
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making what?</font>

350
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be better to have something that
lots of people could see at a glance.</font>

351
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would you measure the 
amount? In numbers? Words?</font>

352
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about people who can't read?</font>

353
00:20:42,170 --> 00:20:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe use colors?</font>

354
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Colors? Would the color change depending 
on the amount of magical energy?</font>

355
00:20:46,930 --> 00:20:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, not exactly...</font>

356
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, is there a material that responds 
to levels of magical energy?</font>

357
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is. It's poisonous,</font>

358
00:20:55,450 --> 00:20:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there's kelsil,
 which expands when exposed.</font>

359
00:20:58,350 --> 00:21:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can be extracted from an ore 
that's often used in magical research.</font>

360
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, if we put it in a 
rectangular mold and let it expand...</font>

361
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if we make it so magical energy
can only contact the bottom?</font>

362
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it'd be forced to expand upward!</font>

363
00:21:12,180 --> 00:21:16,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! And if we can make it so the color
changes with the pressure from that...</font>

364
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have a color guide for magical energy!</font>

365
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it!</font>

366
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's still just a concept...</font>

367
00:21:22,210 --> 00:21:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I can make it with 
the materials in the lab!</font>

368
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not good. It's going to overflow.</font>

369
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

370
00:21:42,730 --> 00:21:45,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's no use. Here it comes.</font>

371
00:21:52,870 --> 00:21:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bro! Watch out!</font>

372
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:40,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 11
I GOT HOSPITALIZED</font>

